title: Revenge of the Iron-Blooded Sword Hound
description: Revenge of the Iron-Blooded Sword Hound He was the hound of the Baskerville family: Vicir. Yet his loyalty was rewarded by the blade of a guillotine dirtied by slander. “I will never live the life of a hound slaughtered after the rabbit is caught.” In place of death, an unexpected opportunity awaits him. Vicir’s eyes glowed red as he sharpened his canines in the dark. “Just you wait, Hugo. I will rip out your throat this time.” It’s time for the hound to exact bloody revenge on his owner. Revenge of the Sword Clan’s Hound
alternative_titles: Revenge of the Iron-Blooded Sword Hound
Revenge of the Sword Clan's Hound
